      My main area of interest is [Metalsmith](https://www.metalsmith.io/) a static site generator that encourages me to learn more about node. Metalsmith has a by-line _An extremely simple, pluggable static site generator_ but that only tells part of the story. At its core, Metalsmith is an "engine" that reads files from a directory, turns them into a javascript object, exposed the object to plugins for manipulation and finally turns the object back into files and writes them to a destination directory. 

